                        <interp inst="t18790915-name-714" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY MORGAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of John Morgan—on 31st July my son brought me a florin, and I went into the shop and found another florin in the till—I found they were bad, and gave them to a policeman.</p>
